\viewkind4\uc1\f0\fs24\b\fs32 FSI Digital - R&D Grant Project Proposal Framework\b0\fs24\par\par
\b 1. Technological Uncertainty (CRA SR&ED Section 1)\b0\par
What are the scientific or technological uncertainties that cannot be resolved using standard public knowledge? Describe the limits of current technologies and why standard developer packages fail.\par\par
\b 2. Systematic Investigation (CRA SR&ED Section 2)\b0\par
Outline the steps of experimental trial and testing. Describe the hypotheses formulated, testing scripts executed, and variations recorded.\par\par
\b 3. Technological Advancement (CRA SR&ED Section 3)\b0\par
What new technological knowledge was generated? Even if the project failed, document what technical constraints were identified.\par\par
}